INSERT INTO `ecs_goods` VALUES (458, 3, 'ECS000458', '原来微信摇一摇是在照顾这些人……', '+', 245, 0, '', 100, 0.000, 426.00, 355.00, 0.00, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '', '', '<p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">网友：以前老爸在北京做生意，在大望路买了套70多平房子，后来生意不好做就回沈阳了，北京的房子就一直出租，因为父母和我都不打算回北京，堂弟毕业打算留北京，我叔全家携我奶就来闹，要用我奶沈阳90平的房子换北京的房子，并且他们没有别的房子，沈阳的房子还要让他们一直住，我家没同意，最后闹到我拘留我叔住院才结束。还有我舅，02年他姑娘上艺校管我妈借5万，我妈没借给了他1万，从此就是仇人了。</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">网友：遇见最离谱的亲戚，让我把新买的笔记本电脑给他，让我再买一个！明明比我大，工资比我高，再打电话就拒接了！后来过年的时候，看他小孩在玩电脑，嘴欠的问了句，这是谁的电脑，结果被回了句，不要你的电脑，我不也有了嘛～～</p><p style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">网友：小时候老家来了几个长辈，说要重修宗祠、家谱。我爸妈其实并不太想弄这些东西，但也不好推辞，就想象征性的交一份就算了，哪里知道这几个老头说你们家算是大户了，应该多交一点。不然连家里冰箱、彩电什么的也给搬走……我在房里听了立马就炸了，冲出来说你们就给我搬搬试试看！原本爸妈要留宿他们的，也被我顶回去，送他们去住了旅馆……</p><p><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"大家身边都有没有一些奇葩亲戚  网友：买房缺首付的那种\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/f1dafa38a37e40708510801434b5635b\" inline=\"0\" img_height=\"180\" img_width=\"632\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">&nbsp;</p><p><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"大家身边都有没有一些奇葩亲戚  网友：买房缺首付的那种\" src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/416b00d648374a74bd2d0cf3506f3fa0\" inline=\"0\" img_height=\"173\" img_width=\"661\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">&nbsp;</p><p><img style=\"margin: 10px auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" alt=\"大家身边都有没有一些奇葩亲戚  网友：买房缺首付的那种\" src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/8a7dc4980bcf4b00858813d0017eead1\" inlin