mal; font-weight: 400; margin-right: 4px; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; speak: none; text-rendering: auto; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\"></em>踩</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; display: block; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">某日，不常登门的姑夫来我家找我爸。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; display: block; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">碰巧我爸和朋友约着去钓鱼去了......</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; display: block; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">我爸在电话里说让姑夫等他，中午在家吃饭，我妈就赶紧张罗着出去买菜之类的。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; display: block; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">眼看着家里只剩下我和姑夫两个人，我本就不懂得人情世故，更怕招待不周，于是走上前去对我说：“我去买菜吧，你在家陪姑夫聊聊”！</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; display: block; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><img style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/756d000702f905a60e67\" img_height=\"368\" img_width=\"454\" fold=\"0\" web_uri=\"756d000702f905a60e67\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; display: block; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28px; font-weight: bold; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">我妈一把把菜蓝子拽过来：“你知道啥啊，上次让你买两个番茄都花了7块钱”！</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; display: block; box-sizing: border-box; -webk