INSERT INTO `ecs_goods` VALUES (499, 1, 'ECS000499', '明星有哪些神回复？', '+', 96, 0, '', 100, 0.250, 237.60, 198.00, 0.00, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '', '', '<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; display: block; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">当然是主持界反应速度最快的汪涵了。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; display: block; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">汪涵年轻的时候并没有学过什么摄影经验，可他居然敢扛着摄影机去《还珠格格》剧组探班，那时候他也没经验，看见人就拍，后来回到家，拿出成片一看，糊了！汪涵能走到今天这个位置，其中原因就是胆大，这才让他抢到了机会。<img style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/1a095000357764054624e\" img_height=\"242\" img_width=\"385\" fold=\"0\" web_uri=\"1a095000357764054624e\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; display: block; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">可是除了胆大，汪涵还心细，他的反应能力太快了，所以汪涵常常就有“神回复”！比如当年节目《天天向上》，汪涵说到公园的老大爷太极打得很好，三环以内直接退回来！<img style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/1a0940003590792f27707\" img_height=\"399\" img_width=\"720\" fold=\"0\" web_uri=\"1a0940003590792f27707\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; display: block; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">欧弟也马上捧哏，他直接问：“那台湾得推几次？”相信欧弟那时候也没有多想，但是汪涵的回复绝了！<img style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/1a095000357617adc2a77\" img_height=\"401\" img_width=\"720\" fold=\"0\" web_uri=\"1a095000357617adc2a77\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; display: block; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">汪涵说。台湾不推，得拉回来！短短一句，回复得十分体面，让人找不到一点毛病。<img style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/1a095000357659d7fe2f1\" img_height=\"336\" img_width=\"600\" fold=\"0\" web_uri=\"1a095000357659d7fe2f1\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; display: block; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">还有汪涵开起车来，那谁也追不到！汪涵在某个综艺上就调侃沈梦辰给男朋友热菜，这句话笑翻全场，相信给位老司机知道这句话什么意思。<img style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/1a09500035768ba362f64\" img_height=\"538\" img_width=\"600\" fold=\"0\" web_uri=\"1a09500035768ba362f64\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; display: block; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">不过今年的跨年汪涵还是破功了，当初孙楠退赛他都没有黑脸，可是今年跨年他的脸是真的黑，完全掩饰不住他心中怒火，或者他根本就没打算掩饰了…………<img style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; display: block; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/1a0910003577c90c5d062\" img_height=\"330\" img_width=\"640\" fold=\"0\" web_uri=\"1a0910003577c90c5d062\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; display: block; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28px; font-weight: bold; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">圈内人，圈内事，我是“青竹乐娱”，关注我，这里有娱乐圈最全资讯！码字不易，记得点赞哦，比心！</span></p><p><a class=\"show-comment\" style=\"background: 0px 0px; outli