yle=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; display: block; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">2.那天骑电动车去大润发，买了个小工具包，等下来的时候发现我这一排车全倒地上，于是本着一颗火热的善良之心，一辆辆都扶了起来。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; display: block; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">旁边有个家伙一直盯着我看，在这连老人都不能扶的年代，我有点怕了，赶紧从工具包里掏出一串钥匙来开锁。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; display: block; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">可是一连开了两次，那锁都没开下来，正郁闷着抬头一看龙头，原来开错了电动车，于是我赶紧找到我那辆，叭，很顺利开了。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; display: block; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">正当我推车要走的时候，那家伙凑上来：喂！哥们，看你这速度，师傅级别。要不交个朋友？有时间探讨探讨……</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; display: block; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">3.回到家我对着镜子仔细的看了又看，</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; display: block; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">我就郁闷：这面相也不象个偷车的啊……</p><p><a class=\"show-comment\" style=\"background: 0px 0px; outline: 0px; transition:color 0.2s; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); line-height: 16px; text-decoration: none; margin-left: 0px; float: left; cursor: pointer; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://www.wukong.com/answer/6662620990855446795/?showComment=6662620990855446795\" target=\"_blank\"><em class=\"bui-icon icon-comments_small\" style=\"color: rgb(202, 202, 202); text-transform: none; line-height: 1; font-family: tticons !important; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box; -we